data.description:
You can't put a new home under your tree this year, but you can put a tree in your new home!  This spacious brick ranch, located in an awesome Urbandale neighborhood, offers a cozy wood burning brick fireplace, a large dining area and the ideal kitchen space for buffet-style parties!   This quiet neighborhood is nestled between Walker Johnson Park, Coronado Park, Dunlap Park/Arboretum and is ideal for walking, accessing trails and shopping.
This home sits on a very large lot and has a couple large picture windows that overlook a spacious backyard that is fully fenced.  Backyard is full of blueberry, raspberry and rose bushes, a peach tree and raised garden beds.  The exterior is maintenance free brick with new metal soffit siding , new roof and updated windows.   This would be a place you could call home for many years!
